{"tid":524400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[齊發聲] 親子王國關注保護兒童意見調查","createTime":"2018-01-09T14:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T14:35:25.000Z","uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7dcbd9d91c859cdf012db513b6d2d6d2fc4d2ce8","tid":524400,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:09:50.000Z","msg":"5歲小朋友臨臨遭受虐待致死的事件令人心痛和髮指！<br />\n<br />\n親子王國現抱住沉重心情，收集國民意見。我們會將1月11日（本星期四）中午12時前收集到的意見綜合整理，並轉發至各大報館，為爸爸媽媽發聲，防止另一慘劇再出現。<br />\n<br />\n為保護兒童出一分力，請即填寫以下問卷！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2CVBXia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2CVBXia&d=L8MSUQG7MI8HI5HnTx9050kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=871aea25\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2CVBXia</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港，唔可以再有多一個受虐兒童！</span>"},{"pid":"b2e58e39f8e0a42b0e023b2d1061447814cc9b09","tid":524400,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"BK出手<br />\n連登都係時候出手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68f03424310dea94e3beb3acffd632cb05e7b33","tid":524400,"uid":10692,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:12:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d7822a916cf6860574869c12bae157877eeddf5","tid":524400,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:27:31.000Z","msg":"國民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7ea676eaac67c2c501e7629ff9affc651dbe65","tid":524400,"uid":12853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:32:35.000Z","msg":"一眾民國民想建國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反了反了"},{"pid":"0260f00b510c48e009dc09ef4a1f8f90b087d028","tid":524400,"uid":165875,"like":0,"dislike"